Path: godot/classes/class_udpserver.rst
Summary: Provides UDP network communication functionality.

UDPServer is a high-level class for handling UDP network communication. It allows you to send and receive UDP packets to and from specific IP addresses and ports.

Inherits: PacketPeer < PacketPeerUniversal < RefCounted
